retrieval.storage.index

Class IndexStructClassic

  • java.lang.Object
    • retrieval.storage.index.IndexStructAbs
      • retrieval.storage.index.IndexStructClassic

  • public final class IndexStructClassic
extends IndexStructAbs
    A visual word index which is implemented by: -simple hashmap for MEMORY config -bdb for BDB config -voldemort for VOLDEMORT config -mysql for a MYSQL config
